data.description: This charming 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom residence is a perfect blend of comfort and coziness. Nestled on a generous .34-acre lot, the property boasts a fenced yard, providing a private oasis for outdoor enjoyment. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of the living room featuring LVP flooring throughout and a cozy wood-burning fireplace - perfect for cool evenings. The well-appointed kitchen is equipped with modern stainless-steel appliances and offers a convenient breakfast room, ideal for casual dining or morning coffee. The roof replacement in 2017 and drain field lines in 2022 are some of the recent upgrades. This home is a perfect balance of tranquility and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
